                  </persName>
            . On the 15th of January, I was walking with Mr. Jones, and in <placeName id="t18240218-13-crimeloc77">St. Ann's-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18240218-13-crimeloc77" type="placeName" value="St. Ann's-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18240218-13-crimeloc77" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240218-13-off75 t18240218-13-crimeloc77"></join>, I felt my pocket very light, turned round, and saw the prisoner crossing towards Bull and Mouth-street - I went over towards him; he immediately took the handkerchief from his bosom, threw it down, and dodged me, but was immediately stopped.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182402180011"></xptr>
            
                  <persName id="t18240218-13-person207">
