                     <interp inst="t18240218-13-person207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Mr. Pearce - the prisoner and a boy were behind him; I had overtook Mr. Pearce - the prisoner 
               <persName id="t18240218-13-person208">drew</persName>
             the boy back from behind him, and soon after Mr. Pearce missed his handkerchief. The prisoner took it, threw it down, and said,</p>
               <p>"I did not take it."</p>
               <p>
            
